HEADWORD: Awkly
<hw>Awk"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In an unlucky
(left-handed) or perverse manner.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Holland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Awkwardly.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
